'''南海仲裁案'''{{NoteTag|全稱為「根据1982年《聯合國海洋法公約》附件七组成的在[[菲律宾共和国|菲律宾共和国]]和[[中华人民共和国|中华人民共和国]]之间的仲裁庭的仲裁（{{lang|en|''An Arbitration before an Arbitral Tribunal constituted under Annex VII to the 1982 United Nations Convention on Law of the Sea between the Republic of the Philippines and the People's Republic of China''}}」）}}<ref>{{cite web |url = https://pcacases.com/web/view/7 |title = The Republic of Philippines v. The People's Republic of China |website = pcacases.com |publisher = [[常设仲裁法院|常设仲裁法院]] |accessdate = 2016-07-12 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160711012503/http://www.pcacases.com/web/view/7 |archivedate = 2016-07-11 }}</ref>，指[[菲律賓共和國|菲律賓共和國]]以[[中華人民共和國|中華人民共和國]]在[[南中國海|南中國海]]（菲律賓称西菲律賓海）中菲争议海域基于“[[九段线|九段线]]”的海洋权益主張及近年的海洋执法和岛礁开发活动已違反《[[聯合國海洋法公約|聯合國海洋法公約]]》（UNCLOS）为由向[[常设仲裁法院|常设仲裁法院]]提出，再由时任庭长柳井俊二與菲律賓根据《[[联合国海洋法公约|联合国海洋法公约]]》附件七任命仲裁人並委請[[常设仲裁法院|常设仲裁法院]]提供场地和秘书服务的临时仲裁庭<ref name="刘建超" />对中华人民共和国提起的[[仲裁|仲裁]]案。

2013年2月19日，中国大陸正式拒绝参与仲裁案，称中国大陸于2006年根据公约第298条作出的声明排除了该公约规定的争端处理机制在海域划界等问题上对中国大陸的适用<ref name="中国排除性声明">{{cite web |url = http://www.un.org/depts/los/convention_agreements/convention_declarations.htm |title = Declarations or Statements upon UNCLOS ratification |accessdate = 2016-07-13 |quote = The Government of the People's Republic of China does not accept any of the procedures provided for in Section 2 of Part XV of the Convention with respect to all the categories of disputes referred to in paragraph 1 (a) (b) and (c) of Article 298 of the Convention. |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160712122702/http://www.un.org/Depts/los/convention_agreements/convention_declarations.htm |archivedate = 2016-07-12 }}</ref><ref name="外交部排除性声明">{{cite web|url=http://www.fmprc.gov.cn/web/ziliao_674904/tytj_674911/tyfg_674913/t270754.shtml|title=中国根据《联合国海洋法公约》第298条提交排除性声明|publisher=[[中华人民共和国外交部|中华人民共和国外交部]]|date=2006-09-07|accessdate=2016-07-15|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160817113303/http://www.fmprc.gov.cn/web/ziliao_674904/tytj_674911/tyfg_674913/t270754.shtml|archivedate=2016-08-17}}</ref>，并认为「此案所涉争端实质上是超出公约调整范围的领土主权和海域划界问题，故仲裁庭对此案无管辖权」<ref name="WuZou2016">{{cite book |author1 = 吴士存 |author2 = 邹克渊 |title = Arbitration Concerning the South China Sea: Philippines versus China |url = http://books.google.com/books?id=lUupCwAAQBAJ |date = 2016-03-02 |publisher=Routledge |ISBN = 978-1-317-17988-7}}</ref>。2014年12月7日，中国大陸发表立场文件阐释在南海仲裁案管辖权问题上的立场<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.csil.cn/News/Detail.aspx?AId=201 |title = The Tribunal's Award in the “South China Sea Arbitration” Initiated by the Philippines Is Null and Void |publisher = 中国国际法学会 |date = 2016-06-10 |accessdate = 2016-07-13 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160822045942/http://www.csil.cn/News/Detail.aspx?AId=201 |archivedate = 2016-08-22 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.gov.cn/xinwen/2014-12/07/content_2787671.htm |title = 中华人民共和国政府关于菲律宾共和国所提南海仲裁案管辖权问题的立场文件摘要 |publisher = [[中华人民共和国外交部|中华人民共和国外交部]] |date = 2014-12-07 |accessdate = 2016-07-13 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160919053502/http://www.gov.cn/xinwen/2014-12/07/content_2787671.htm |archivedate = 2016-09-19 }}</ref>。

2015年7月7日，仲裁庭舉行首次[[聽證會|聽證會]]；而[[中華人民共和國外交部|中華人民共和國外交部]]同時發表聲明，不承認仲裁庭對此案的[[司法管轄權|司法管轄權]]，也拒絕菲律賓任何形式有關此案的和解提議<ref name="reuters">{{cite news |first = Toby |last = Sterling |title = South China Sea dispute between China, Philippines heads to court |url = http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/07/07/us-southchinasea-arbitration-idUSKCN0PH1KH20150707 |accessdate = 2015-07-07 |agency = [[路透社|路透社]] |date = 2015-07-07 |language = en |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150708051125/http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/07/07/us-southchinasea-arbitration-idUSKCN0PH1KH20150707 |archivedate = 2015-07-08 }}</ref>。10月29日，仲裁庭正式裁定對此案菲律賓提出的7项诉求拥有管辖权，并将对菲律賓其他诉求的管辖权裁定留待审理时作出<ref name=PCA20151029>{{cite web |title = Award on Jurisdiction and Admissibility 29102015 |publisher = [[常设仲裁法院|常设仲裁法院]] |date = 2015-10-29 |pages = 149 |url = http://www.pcacases.com/web/sendAttach/1506 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160716154440/http://www.pcacases.com/web/sendAttach/1506 |archivedate = 2016-07-16 |access-date = 2016-07-13 }}</ref>。

2016年7月12日，在中国大陸[[缺席審判|缺席]]的情況下，仲裁庭公布仲裁结果，支持菲律宾在此案相关问题<!-- 并非岛礁主权归属 -->上的几乎全部诉求<ref name="纽约时报">{{cite web |url = http://www.nytimes.com/2016/07/13/world/asia/south-china-sea-hague-ruling-philippines.html |title = Hague Tribunal Rejects Beijing's Claims in South China Sea |date = 2016-07-13 |publisher = [[纽约时报|纽约时报]] |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160713064120/http://www.nytimes.com/2016/07/13/world/asia/south-china-sea-hague-ruling-philippines.html |archivedate = 2016-07-13 |accessdate = 2016-07-12 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/jul/12/philippines-wins-south-china-sea-case-against-china |title = Philippines wins South China Sea case against China |first1 = Tom |last1 = Phillips |first2 = Oliver |last2 = Holmes |first3 = Owen |last3 = Bowcott |date = 2016-07-12 |publisher = [[卫报|卫报]] |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160712120247/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/jul/12/philippines-wins-south-china-sea-case-against-china |archivedate = 2016-07-12 |accessdate = 2016-07-12 }}</ref>。仲裁庭5名仲裁员一致裁定，在《聯合國海洋法公約》下中国大陸对南海自然资源不享有基于“[[九段线|九段线]]”的历史性权利<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.cnn.com/2016/07/12/asia/china-philippines-south-china-sea/index.html |title = South China Sea: Philippines wins Hague court ruling |first = Katie |last = Hunt |publisher = [[CNN|CNN]] |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160712150343/http://www.cnn.com/2016/07/12/asia/china-philippines-south-china-sea/index.html |archivedate = 2016-07-12 |accessdate = 2016-07-12 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-36771749 |title = South China Sea: Tribunal backs case against China brought by Philippines - BBC News |publisher = [[英国广播公司|BBC]] |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160712142552/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-36771749 |archivedate = 2016-07-12 |accessdate = 2016-07-12 }}</ref>。仲裁庭还認定中国大陸在南海的[[填海造陆|填海造陆]]“给环境造成了不可挽回的损失”，并要求中国大陸停止在南海的活动<ref name="纽约时报" /><ref name="仲裁庭">{{Cite web|url=https://pca-cpa.org/en/news/pca-press-release-the-south-china-sea-arbitration-the-republic-of-the-philippines-v-the-peoples-republic-of-china/|title=PCA Press Release: The South China Sea Arbitration (The Republic of the Philippines v. The People’s Republic of China) {{!}} PCA-CPA|website=pca-cpa.org|access-date=2016-07-12|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160712091907/https://pca-cpa.org/en/news/pca-press-release-the-south-china-sea-arbitration-the-republic-of-the-philippines-v-the-peoples-republic-of-china/|archivedate=2016-07-12}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=http://www.dw.com/zh/%E6%B5%B7%E7%89%99%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%9C%A8%E5%8D%97%E6%B5%B7%E4%B8%8D%E4%BA%AB%E6%9C%89%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2%E6%80%A7%E6%9D%83%E5%88%A9/a-19394901?&zhongwen=trad|title=海牙：中国在南海不享有“历史性权利”|accessdate=2017-03-08|author=|date=2016-12-07|last=|first=|work=DW.COM|publisher=Deutsche Welle|language=zh|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170309073026/http://www.dw.com/zh/%E6%B5%B7%E7%89%99%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%9C%A8%E5%8D%97%E6%B5%B7%E4%B8%8D%E4%BA%AB%E6%9C%89%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2%E6%80%A7%E6%9D%83%E5%88%A9/a-19394901?&zhongwen=trad|archivedate=2017-03-09}}</ref>。

